nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Good morning, Person1, I want to cancel or at least postpone my appointment for the bone density injection. I not sure if Dr. Person2 was aware that I about to undergo some extensive dental work at the Org3 and I understand that the bone density treatment could be detrimental to my current regimen which is working so well. Please reply when you can with your opinion. Many thanks!
